T*
() Tj
T*
(The script accepts --key value pairs and dispatches by --step.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Supported steps:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(-   SetupMetadata) Tj
T*
(-   IngestBronze) Tj
T*
(-   Scd2Silver) Tj
ET
endstream
