(-   overwrite metadata_config) Tj
T*
(-   overwrite dq_rules) Tj
T*
(-   create dq_issues_log if absent) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Flow:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(    validate mongodb_uri) Tj
T*
(      -> CREATE SCHEMA IF NOT EXISTS) Tj
T*
(      -> WRITE metadata_config \(overwrite\)) Tj
T*
(      -> WRITE dq_rules \(overwrite\)) Tj
T*
(      -> CREATE dq_issues_log IF NOT EXISTS) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.3 IngestBronze Step) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Responsibilities:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(-   load active source configuration from metadata) Tj
T*
(-   read source records from MongoDB \(via pymongo\)) Tj
T*
(-   normalize data types and required columns) Tj
T*
(-   append into Bronze Delta table) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Normalization contract:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(-   cast to deterministic types) Tj
T*
(-   fallback updated_at to current timestamp) Tj
T*
(-   map _id to source_document_id) Tj
T*
(-   filter out null customer_id) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Flow:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(    read metadata_config active row) Tj
T*
(      -> resolve effective mongo uri) Tj
T*
(      -> load source docs) Tj
T*
(      -> normalize_source\(\)) Tj
T*
(      -> append to bronze_customers) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
