40 792 Td
(-   compute record_hash for change detection) Tj
T*
(-   close current records when changes detected) Tj
T*
(-   insert new current versions) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Flow:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(    ensure silver table exists) Tj
T*
(      -> read bronze) Tj
T*
(      -> latest record per customer_id) Tj
T*
(      -> compare hash vs current silver) Tj
T*
(         -> close changed current rows \(is_current=false, valid_to=merge_ts\)) Tj
T*
(         -> insert new current rows \(is_current=true, valid_from=merge_ts\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.5 DqEngine Step) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Responsibilities:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(-   read active DQ rules from dq_rules) Tj
T*
(-   evaluate each rule against current Silver records) Tj
T*
(-   collect failed rows per rule) Tj
T*
(-   append failures to dq_issues_log) Tj
T*
(-   optionally fail task if dq_fail_on_issues=true) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Flow:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(    load active silver + active rules) Tj
T*
(      -> for each rule:) Tj
T*
(           filter rows violating rule_sql) Tj
T*
(           build issue rows with payload) Tj
T*
(      -> append issues to dq_issues_log) Tj
T*
(      -> if failures and strict mode: raise [DQ_VALIDATION_FAILED]) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.6 DQ Operational Modes) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(-   warn mode \(dq_fail_on_issues=false\): logs issues and completes) Tj
T*
(-   strict mode \(dq_fail_on_issues=true\): logs issues and fails DqEngine) Tj
T*
(    task) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This is intentional behavior, not a platform failure.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
