T*
() Tj
T*
(Modes:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(-   reset_and_seed: recreates clean baseline dataset) Tj
T*
(-   add_good: inserts valid incremental records) Tj
T*
(-   add_bad: inserts records designed to fail DQ rules) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Flow:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(    parse --mode and mongo uri) Tj
T*
(      -> connect to ecommerce.customers) Tj
T*
(      -> execute selected operation) Tj
T*
(      -> close client) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Purpose:) Tj
ET
