() Tj
T*
(1.  Metadata-Driven Configuration Pattern) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(-   ingestion behavior controlled by metadata tables) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2.  Medallion Layering \(Bronze/Silver\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(-   raw-normalized capture then curated SCD2) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.  SCD Type 2 Historical Modeling) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(-   full historical lineage of customer changes) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.  Rule Engine Pattern) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(-   externalized SQL predicates in dq_rules) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5.  Strategy-like Provider Routing) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(-   runtime LLM provider selection with provider-specific implementation) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6.  Fail-Fast / Fail-Open Toggle) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(-   configurable strict or warning mode for DQ enforcement) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj
